name: CASCA-MIX
description:
Cute Anime semi-realistic creepy art

Took me a while with my blending machine to create this checkpoint. capable of producing a wide range of artistic creations. From adorable anime illustrations to chilling horror scenes.

Positive prompts:

  • (masterpiece:1.2), (high resolution:1.2), (best quality:1.1), (HDR), (cinematic lighting), (sharp focus), I'm using this as my base style.

  • (creepy anatomy), (horror illustration) for creepy stuff.

Neg prompts:

  • (worst quality, bad quality:1.3), (watermark) (label) (signature) (text), I'm using this as my base style as well.

I'm experimenting with different Prompt Embeddings and Lora, so far looks good!
